      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a reliable daily driver at an affordable price point. The engine and transmission are functional, though the car shows its age with some cosmetic imperfections, including minor scratches on the exterior and some wear on the interior upholstery. There are a few minor mechanical items that will likely need attention soon, such as a slightly worn suspension and older tires, but the car remains roadworthy and starts every time. It has been maintained regularly, though it is no longer in pristine condition. This is an honest, high-mileage vehicle that still has life left in it for the right owner.",
