    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a turn-key example for the discerning purist. Powered by the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies, the powertrain delivers linear throttle response up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement with ARP bolts, and a structural subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains rigid and communicative, riding on pristine Style 67 wheels. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic with an immaculate Nappa leather interior, this specimen exhibits zero paint fade or bolster wear, maintaining its factory-correct tolerances and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
