      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a mirror-like finish, entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is original with perfect gaps and a clean history. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no visible bolster wear, the dashboard is crack-free, and all electronics function with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is peerless, featuring a comprehensive service portfolio with every maintenance milestone documented at authorized specialists. The engine bay is detailed to a professional standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is an uncompromising example for a buyer who demands the absolute best in quality and provenance.",
